== Parsers with Auto Scroll ==

When using the Modernized theme, double-clicking any line within the content of this page or on any of the items below will auto-scroll the edit textarea to the line clicked. 

The Basic theme increases the edit textarea size to hold all content so the textarea does not have a scrollbar. In this case, the caret will be correctly positioned within the textarea, but the window will not automatically scroll to make the caret visible. Pressing the keyboard right-arrow key will scroll the window so the caret is visible at the bottom.

Because of the way the Markdown parser is constructed, it is frequently not possible to calculate an accurate line number in the text source. This causes auto-scroll to miss the target text. The error can be minimized by consistent use of one blank line between text blocks.

